channel.title: Need some Command help?
channel.description:
Okay, So I have Test Scape and I've just been playing it and when I type ::servermenu it brings up alot of the commands and everything, well it says the autospawn commands are "DISABLED"....so does anyone know how I go in and enable them? So I can get full dragon and stuff?
Please Post here.

item.title: Need some Command help?
item.dc:creator: @bugra bugra
item.description:
@bugra wrote:

if (command.startsWith("dragon") && playerRights >= 2) { addItem(item idhow many); }

Hope this helps you
